title: #72- Nadeshot & Envoy Reveal Worst Part of Teaming with Scump
itunes:title: #72- Nadeshot & Envoy Reveal Worst Part of Teaming with Scump
description: On this episode of The CouRage and Nadeshot Show podcast, LA Thieves' very own Dylan "Envoy" Hannon comes onto the show to talk about getting dropped from OpTic Texas, joining LA Thieves, teaming with Scump, CoD Vanguard, Warzone, Halo Infinite's early success, and more!
